dom_names
======================
This plugin added three ActiveRecord::Base instance methods to simplify work with ajax or css.

USES:
======================
AR instance methods:
- dom_id
- dom_class
- dom_path

dom_id
=======================
@post = Post.find(1)
@post.dom_id                    => post_1
@post.dom_id(favorite)          => favorite_post_1
@post.dom_id(favorite, deleted) => favorite_post_1_deleted

dom_path
=======================
@post.dom_path  => posts

dom_class
=======================
@post.dom_class            => post
@post.dom_class(new)       => new_post
@post.dom_class("", false) => posts




